First, I have two files: offices.csv and homes.csv. Each of these has two text columns. The offices file has 'employee_id' and 'work_address', while the homes file has 'employee_id' and 'home_address'. My goal is to join these two tables on the employee_id so that each row in the result contains both the work and home addresses for employees who exist in both files.

